    <para>Attached schemas and standard formally define exchange format for invoices and other types of documents. The
        format was originally created by Working Group for Electronic Data
        Interchange Standards of <link xlink:href="http://www.ictu.cz/">ICT Unie o.s.</link>.
        As of now future development and maintenance is done by Ministry of the Interior.</para>
    <para>Inquires can be sent to <email>info@isdoc.cz</email>.</para>
